Popular Nigerian actress, Etinosa Idemudia in an interview on TVC WakeUpNigeria talks about abuse from internet trolls and how celebrities are human. Etinosa said she started replying trolls to defend herself and for people to know that celebrities are human beings with feelings. The actress said she is against the notation that celebrities shouldn’t reply to social media abuse like big head, stupid and so on. Etinosa said she reply to show her human self. She said: “Everything about me is highly spiritual like my outer ego, the trouble maker that many people know comes when there is a trigger. Source